---
/**
 * bloom-filters · 0002-sizing-a-bloom-filter · Figure 1 — "Two inputs decide everything".
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from docs/bloom-filters/lessons/0002-sizing-a-bloom-filter.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). It lives as an .astro component, NOT inline in the
 * MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with raw inline SVG that uses
 * kebab-case attributes (text-anchor, font-size, stroke-width, marker-end, …) and
 * self-referential ids. In an .astro file the SVG is plain HTML, so it renders
 * byte-for-byte. The SVG marker id (a) is kept as-is to match the source DOM.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        viewBox="0 0 680 300"
        font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif"
    >
        <defs
            ><marker
                id="a"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0 0L10 5L0 10z" fill="#136f63"></path></marker
            ></defs
        >
        <rect width="680" height="300" fill="#fffff8"></rect>
        <text x="340" y="28" text-anchor="middle" font-size="15" fill="#0f4f47" font-weight="bold"
            >Two inputs decide everything</text
        >
        <rect x="16" y="70" width="150" height="46" rx="8" fill="#e8f1ef" stroke="#136f63"></rect>
        <text x="91" y="92" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" fill="#0f4f47">n = # items</text>
        <text x="91" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f"
            >how many you store</text
        >
        <rect x="16" y="170" width="150" height="46" rx="8" fill="#e8f1ef" stroke="#136f63"></rect>
        <text x="91" y="192" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" fill="#0f4f47">p = target FP</text>
        <text x="91" y="208" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f"
            >error you accept</text
        >
        <rect x="200" y="60" width="256" height="56" rx="8" fill="#fff" stroke="#9a7a17"></rect>
        <text x="328" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="15" fill="#7a5e12"
            >m = &#8722;(n &#183; ln p) / (ln 2)&#178;</text
        >
        <text x="328" y="104" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f"
            >bit-array size &#8212; uses n AND p</text
        >
        <rect x="200" y="170" width="256" height="56" rx="8" fill="#fff" stroke="#2f5d3a"></rect>
        <text x="328" y="194" text-anchor="middle" font-size="15" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >k = log&#8322;(1 / p)</text
        >
        <text x="328" y="214" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f"
            >hash count &#8212; uses p ONLY</text
        >
        <rect x="496" y="64" width="168" height="48" rx="8" fill="#fbf3e6" stroke="#9a7a17"></rect>
        <text x="580" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#7a5e12"
            >bit-array size m</text
        >
        <text x="580" y="102" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f">grows with n</text>
        <rect x="496" y="174" width="168" height="48" rx="8" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></rect>
        <text x="580" y="194" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#2f5d3a"># hashes k</text>
        <text x="580" y="212" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#6b675f"
            >fixed by p alone</text
        >
        <path
            d="M166 90 L200 86"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#136f63"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            marker-end="url(#a)"></path>
        <path
            d="M166 193 L200 198"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#136f63"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            marker-end="url(#a)"></path>
        <path
            d="M120 170 C150 150 170 130 200 110"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#136f63"
            stroke-width="1.2"
            stroke-dasharray="4 3"
            marker-end="url(#a)"></path>
        <path
            d="M456 88 L496 88"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#9a7a17"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            marker-end="url(#a)"></path>
        <path
            d="M456 198 L496 198"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#2f5d3a"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            marker-end="url(#a)"></path>
        <rect x="200" y="252" width="256" height="34" rx="6" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></rect>
        <text x="328" y="274" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#2f5d3a" font-weight="bold"
            >k ignores n &#8212; double the items, same k</text
        >
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Choose <code>p</code>, count <code>n</code>; the two formulas hand you <code>m</code> and
        <code>k</code>.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
